EN: They set an ambush at the intersection.

ZH: 我们注意到周围有人可能在埋伏我们。
EN: We noticed someone around us possibly ambushing us.

ZH: 队伍遭到了埋伏，损失惨重。
EN: The team fell into an ambush and suffered heavy casualties.

