EN: The guerrilla troops carried out ambush operations in the forest.

ZH: 她躲在树丛中进行埋伏。
EN: She hid in the bushes to set up an ambush.

ZH: 埋伏圈不断缩小，我们的困境越来越严峻。
EN: The ambush perimeter is shrinking, and our predicament is becoming more severe.

ZH: 即使受到埋伏，我们也不会退缩。
EN: Even if we are ambushed, we will not back down.

ZH: 在敌人的埋伏下，我们被迫撤退。
